        <sponsor name-id="C000059">Mr. Calvert</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="R000592">Mr. Rokita</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="N000181">Mr. Nunes</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="C001095">Mr. Cotton</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="G000377">Ms. Granger</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="I000056">Mr. Issa</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HAS00">Committee on Armed Services</committee-name>
